    <text>
        <body>
            <div style="handwritten" type="letter" xml:id="d.1">
                <head type="title">Miklós Oláh to Tamás Nádasdy (Augsburg, 13 February 1551)</head>
                <floatingText type="regesta">
                    <body>
                        <p xml:id="reg.p.1">The news János Fejérthóy brought has turned out to be
                            untrue. All of Germania is at peace; the people of Magdeburg have lost
                            hope, Maurice, Electory of Saxony is attacking them. The Hungarians will
                            get the support. Oláh will be three days ahead of the King, who will
                            leave 6-8 days later, together with Maximilian. Queen Mary will return
                            to Flanders straight after that, while the Emperor will stay here. Oláh
                            presented Ferenc Batthyány’s wife here on the 10<hi rend="super"
                            >th</hi>.</p>
                    </body>
                </floatingText>
                <pb/>
                <p xml:id="p.1">Spectabilis et Magnifice Domine et Frater Observandissime,
                    servitiorum meorum commendationem!</p>
                <p xml:id="p.2">Querelae et rumores, de quibus <persName>Feyerthoy</persName><note
                        type="critic" xml:id="note.1">János Fejérthóy.</note> nomine Dominationis
                    Vestrae Magnificae locutus fuit, vanae sunt. Nihil eorum certum est. </p>
                <p xml:id="p.3">Tota Germaniae pars in quiete silet. Magdeburgenses quoque sunt in
                    desperatione. <persName>Mauritius</persName><note type="critic" xml:id="note.2"
                        >Maurice, Elector of Saxony.</note> dux arcta eos urget obsidione non paucis
                    equitum et peditum viribus speratum illorum itaque aut deditio aut expugnatio.
                    Hic omnia ex voto caesaris et regis confecta iam fere sunt, <add
                        corresp="Olahus" type="insert">subsidium habebitis</add>, affinitates adhuc
                    secretae sunt. Ego obtenta <del corresp="Olahus">ut</del> iam tandem venia
                    praecedam <add corresp="Olahus" type="insert">ad
                        triduum</add><persName>maiestatem regiam</persName>, quae sexto vel octavo
                    post die sequetur cum <persName>Maximiliano</persName> rege. Serenissima regina
                        <persName>Maria</persName> statim post discessum regium revertetur in
                    Flandriam. <persName>Caesar</persName> hic aliquandiu manebit. Dominam
                        <persName>coniugem</persName><note type="critic" xml:id="note.3">Katalin
                        Svetkovics.</note> domini <persName>Bothyany</persName><note type="critic"
                        xml:id="note.4">Ferenc Batthyány.</note> cum honore 10. huius mensis die
                        <add corresp="Olahus" type="insert">huc</add> introduci feci. De rebus
                    omnibus <add corresp="Olahus" type="insert">aliis</add>, de quibus Dominatio
                    Vestra ad me scripsit, non contemnendum reporto responsum, de quo citavi plura.
                    Dominatio Vestra cum domina <persName>coniuge</persName><note type="critic"
                        xml:id="note.5">Orsolya Kanizsai.</note> sua carissima, domina mea
                    observandissima feliciter valeat.</p>
                <p xml:id="p.4">Ex <placeName>Augusta</placeName> 13. Februarii anno 1551.</p>
                <p xml:id="p.5">
                    <seg type="signature">Servitor Agriensis manu sua.</seg>
                </p>
                <p xml:id="p.6">Surculos regina exspectat.<note type="critic" xml:id="note.6">See
                        Ep. 757., and Ep.
                        761.<ref>olahus.tei.15510106_1</ref></note><ref>/o:olahus.tei.15510127_1</ref></p>
                <pb/>
            </div>
            <div style="handwritten" type="verso" xml:id="d.2">
                <head>On the outer side:</head>
                <p xml:id="p.7">Domino comiti Thomae Nadasdi etc.</p>
            </div>
